                <div class="essential">
                    <h4>Clears the Air</h4>
                    <p class="text-justify">Between co-founders many matters tend to go undiscussed. This agreement gives the early team members the opportunity to discuss these matters, clearing any doubts and allowing for a better relationship.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="essential">
                    <h4>Defines Roles</h4>
                    <p class="text-justify">This gives members the opportunity to clarify their role in the company and also gives every founding member a good understanding of what the other founding members do.</p>
                </div>
